      <title>香港数十年来首批记者因煽动罪被定罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/hong-kong-convicts-first-journalists-for-sedition-in-decades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港一家法院判处两名前编辑因发表涉嫌煽动性文章有罪，这是几十年来首次以煽动叛乱罪判处记者有罪，此举可能加深人们对新闻自由的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/hong-kong-convicts-first-journalists-for-sedition-in-decades</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 07:46:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其邀请海湾国家竞标 200 亿美元新贸易路线</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/turkey-hosts-development-road-talks-with-gulf-nations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其周四在伊斯坦布尔接待了伊拉克、卡塔尔和阿联酋的交通部长，讨论建设连接波斯湾和欧洲的一条价值约 200 亿美元的贸易路线。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/turkey-hosts-development-road-talks-with-gulf-nations</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 07:38:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾计划购买 40 架战机，因中菲争端蔓延至空域</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/philippines-plans-to-buy-40-jets-as-china-spat-reaches-airspace</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾国防部长星期四表示，菲律宾计划购买 40 架新型多用途战斗机，以增强其军事能力，以应对最近与中国在领空发生的敌对行为。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/philippines-plans-to-buy-40-jets-as-china-spat-reaches-airspace</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 06:34:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯里兰卡左翼候选人通过反腐运动取得进展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/sri-lanka-leftist-candidate-akd-gains-ground-in-election-on-anti-corruption-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位有着斯里兰卡马克思主义社会主义政策根基的候选人在下个月的总统选举中获得了支持，他强烈要求打击腐败并仔细审查与中国的投资交易，以避免再次陷入债务陷阱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/sri-lanka-leftist-candidate-akd-gains-ground-in-election-on-anti-corruption-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 05:09:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>与以色列的战争威胁重新定义了贝鲁特的“正常”生活</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/israel-hamas-war-threat-looms-over-beirut-as-israel-and-hezbollah-clash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[黎巴嫩首都长期以来一直是冲突的代名词。现在，再次爆发冲突的可能性又开始显现。]]></description>
